| Reward and Pleasure         | Induces pleasure, chills, motivation to listen  | Dopamine, endogenous opioids                         | Salimpoor et al. (2011)            |
| Cognitive Performance       | Enhances creativity and focus (at moderate levels) | Optimal arousal via autonomic nervous system         | Mehta et al. (2012)                |
